<p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/cost-accounting/terms-cost-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="145">Formula allocation bases let you define advanced formulas to achieve the correct allocation basis. You can manually create formula allocation bases. You can use the following operators to define your formula.</p>
